                </solution>           </exercise><exercise xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:q="http://cnx.rice.edu/qml/1.0" id="sq1302_ex05" type="section-quiz"><problem id="fs-id3025742">
                    <para id="import-auto-id1169033099071">In the United States, life expectancy rates in recent decades have ______.</para>
                    <list id="sq05" list-type="enumerated" number-style="lower-alpha"><item>continued to gradually rise</item>
                        <item>gone up and down due to global issues such as military conflicts</item>
                        <item>lowered as healthcare improves</item>
                        <item>stayed the same since the mid-1960s</item>
